<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3985528>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Parasites found in the American red-eared slider, Trachemys scripta in eastern Spain. (A) Telorchis solivagus; (B) Serpinema microcephalus (anterior part detail); (C) Neopolystoma orbiculare (immature); (D) Neopolystoma orbiculare (adult). Scale bars: A, B, D, 1 mm; C, 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3985528/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

